<p>The <code>even</code> property matches even iterations (2nd, 4th, etc.).</p>

<pre>{open}users{close}
  &lt;tr{open}property:even{close} style="background:#f0f0f0"{open}/property:even{close}&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;{open}$name{close}&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<h3>Result:</h3>
<table border="1" cellpadding="5">
{users}
  <tr{property:even} style="background:#f0f0f0"{/property:even}>
    <td>{$name}</td>
  </tr>
{/users}
</table>
